It' a crime for it not to be returnable.p.s. My favorite offering was labeled "Dark Chocolate Covered Raisins" , last ordered on May 24 this year.For some reason it seems no longer available.

name: James L. Moore
title: These are NOT Greek Yogurt - they are VERY sugary
review: I ordered the Greek Yogurt covered ones.Unfortunately, no nutritional label was provided in the listing, so I just assumed that's what they were.These claim to be a "Greek yogurt flavored coating" where the FIRST ingredient is sugar.In other words, they are NOT Greek yogurt covered.Greek yogurt is tangy, not sweet, and is a healthy snack.These are junk food candy, and they taste horrible.
